### School Management API - Test Requests

### ============================================
### STUDENT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get All Students
GET https://localhost:5001/api/students

### Get Student by ID
GET https://localhost:5001/api/students/S001

### Create Student (All fields)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S001",
  "name": "John",
  "surname": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "2005-05-15",
  "city": "New York",
  "street": "123 Main St",
  "postalCode": "10001"
}

### Create Student (Required fields only)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S002",
  "name": "Jane",
  "surname": "Smith",
  "dateOfBirth": "2006-03-20"
}

### Create Another Student
POST https://localhost:5001/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S003",
  "name": "Bob",
  "surname": "Johnson",
  "dateOfBirth": "2005-08-10",
  "city": "Boston"
}

### Try to create duplicate student (should fail)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S001",
  "name": "Another",
  "surname": "Person",
  "dateOfBirth": "2005-01-01"
}

### Update Student
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/students/S001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "surname": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "2005-05-15",
  "city": "Los Angeles",
  "street": "456 New Ave",
  "postalCode": "90001"
}

### Delete Student
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/students/S003

### ============================================
### SCHOOL CLASS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get All Classes
GET https://localhost:5001/api/classes

### Get Class by ID
GET https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1

### Create Class
POST https://localhost:5001/api/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Class 5A",
  "leadingTeacher": "Mrs. Smith"
}

### Create Another Class
POST https://localhost:5001/api/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Class 5B",
  "leadingTeacher": "Mr. Johnson"
}

### Update Class
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Class 5A Advanced",
  "leadingTeacher": "Mrs. Smith-Brown"
}

### Delete Class
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/classes/2

### ============================================
### CLASS-STUDENT ASSIGNMENT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Add Student to Class
POST https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S001"
}

### Add Another Student to Class
POST https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S002"
}

### Try to add same student again (should fail)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S001"
}

### Remove Student from Class
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/classes/1/students/S002

